v1.0-ALPHA
----------

[jan] Add preferences interface.
[jan] Allow loading of any applications from the menu.
[jan] Add Polish translation (Tadeusz Lesiecki <lesiecki@tmtsystem.pl>, Piotr
      Tarnowski <drfugazi@drfugazi.eu.org>).
